00:29:46.632 --> 00:29:47.850
I'm Michael.

273
00:29:47.894 --> 00:29:48.982
Alex.

274
00:29:49.025 --> 00:29:51.941
Alex.

275
00:29:51.985 --> 00:29:55.379
Well, Alex, maybe sometime
