295
00:31:22.205 --> 00:31:24.860
I... don't remember.

296
00:31:24.904 --> 00:31:26.079
Well, thanks.

297
00:31:26.122 --> 00:31:27.950
Yeah, no problem.
Hey...


298
00:31:27.994 --> 00:31:29.778
You OK?

299
00:31:29.822 --> 00:31:32.085
Yeah. Fine.

300
00:32:06.989 --> 00:32:08.774
You could bottle that stuff

301
