of people who would try it.


303
00:32:14.040 --> 00:32:18.131
Yeah, but then they'd
want it all the time.


304
00:32:19.480 --> 00:32:21.080
So it looks like they
might be setting up


305
00:32:21.105 --> 00:32:23.223
the old carnival out there?

306
00:32:23.266 --> 00:32:25.268
I doubt it.

307
00:32:25.312 --> 00:32:30.143
There hasn't been a carnival
out there in over 20 years.


308
00:33:06.396 --> 00:33:08.224
Sid?

309
00:33:16.842 --> 00:33:18.974
Who's there?

310
00:33:29.985 --> 00:33:32.771
Who's there?

311
00:33:45.784 --> 00:33:47.524
No...

312
00:33:48.787 --> 00:33:50.484
No what?

313
00:33:52.878 --> 00:33:55.315
Nothing.

314
00:34:53.895 --> 00:34:56.115
Wanna know what
little girls are made of?


315
00:34:56.158 --> 00:35:01.294
Sugar and spice
and everything nice.


316
00:35:08.518 --> 00:35:09.171
Get away!

317
00:35:09.215 --> 00:35:11.913
Alex! Stop!
