321
00:35:22.576 --> 00:35:26.232
Can you breathe now?

322
00:36:13.322 --> 00:36:16.238
Where did this come from?

323
00:36:16.282 --> 00:36:17.544
Told you...

324
00:36:17.587 --> 00:36:19.467
I know what you told me.
Where did it come from?


325
00:36:19.492 --> 00:36:22.375
I don't know, Alex.
I never saw it before last night.


326
00:36:22.418 --> 00:36:24.812
You didn't see anybody
leave it on the bar?


327
00:36:24.855 --> 00:36:26.901
Nobody handed it to you?

328
00:36:26.945 --> 00:36:29.817
Yes. You did.

329
00:36:32.602 --> 00:36:34.865
Is it bad?

330
00:36:35.954 --> 00:36:39.479
I don't know what it is.

331
00:36:46.007 --> 00:36:49.706
How'd you like to drink
for free tonight?


332
00:36:51.752 --> 00:36:55.625
Sounds like you need a favor.

333
00:36:56.278 --> 00:36:58.585
I do.

334
00:37:00.587 --> 00:37:02.763
This the guy?

335
00:37:02.806 --> 00:37:04.634
