344
00:37:34.664 --> 00:37:37.841
and sentenced to life in prison.

345
00:37:37.885 --> 00:37:38.929
Yeah, I know that.

346
00:37:38.973 --> 00:37:40.409
I'm sure you do.

347
00:37:40.453 --> 00:37:43.934
The report says it was your
