362
00:38:28.849 --> 00:38:31.199
I am not crazy.

363
00:38:31.243 --> 00:38:32.331
I'm sorry, Alex.

364
00:38:32.374 --> 00:38:35.290
I don't know what
I can do to help you.


365
00:38:44.386 --> 00:38:46.171
