It's all right here.

427
00:43:33.806 --> 00:43:37.592
And no one can take that
away from you.


428
00:43:41.117 --> 00:43:44.425
I'm not ready to go.

429
00:43:45.165 --> 00:43:47.863
I know.

430
00:43:48.429 --> 00:43:52.172
But you're closer
than you think.


431
00:43:55.480 --> 00:43:58.004
And until then...

432
00:43:59.353 --> 00:44:03.052
I guess we'll just have
to stick around here...


433
00:44:03.096 --> 00:44:07.883
Till you feel like you can
take those memories with you.


434
00:44:12.627 --> 00:44:17.893
In the meantime,
why don't you take it easy tonight?


435
00:44:17.937 --> 00:44:18.938
But the bar...

436
00:44:18.981 --> 00:44:21.506
I'll worry about the bar.

437
00:44:21.549 --> 00:44:24.944
I owe you one, anyways.

438
00:44:30.123 --> 00:44:32.473
Thanks.

439
00:47:52.412 --> 00:47:55.110
Hey, get out of here!

440
00:47:55.154 --> 00:47:58.070
You're not ready yet!

441
00:48:12.214 --> 00:48:13.999
Let me out of here!

442
00:48:50.949 --> 00:48:53.647
Hi, Dr. Goldfine, please?

443
00:48:53.691 --> 00:48:58.565
Yes, this is Alex Grant.
I'm a patient of his.


444
00:48:58.608 --> 00:49:01.786
Yes, I need to see him again.

445
00:49:02.047 --> 00:49:05.703
No, no, I... I don't...

446
00:49:06.181 --> 00:49:09.054
I can't wait that long.

447
00:49:10.098 --> 00:49:13.798
Fine.
Yeah, I understand.


448
00:49:18.019 --> 00:49:20.761
Yeah. I
-I'll do that.

