a melancholy maiden?

453
00:49:38.257 --> 00:49:40.172
But not yet!

454
00:49:40.215 --> 00:49:42.261
Wanna do my makeup?

455
00:49:42.304 --> 00:49:45.960
But your face is already done.

456
00:49:46.656 --> 00:49:50.878
We're not gonna do my face.

457
00:50:17.296 --> 00:50:18.514
Thanks.

458
00:50:18.558 --> 00:50:19.820
Yeah.

459
00:50:19.864 --> 00:50:22.344
Listen,
I'm sorry I snapped at you last night.


