00:50:22.388 --> 00:50:26.087
I
-I'm just kind of...

461
00:50:26.653 --> 00:50:29.656
Hey. It's all right.

462
00:50:29.699 --> 00:50:33.268
I know you've been having
a hard time.


463
00:50:33.965 --> 00:50:36.271
It's gonna be OK, though.

464
00:50:36.315 --> 00:50:39.448
I hope you know that.

465
00:50:40.275 --> 00:50:42.190
Thanks.

466
00:50:42.234 --> 00:50:45.890
Look, let me get you
some more longnecks.


467
00:50:54.594 --> 00:50:57.510
Alex?

468
00:51:03.777 --> 00:51:06.475
You doing OK?

469
00:51:07.650 --> 00:51:09.043
Me?

