00:51:21.751 --> 00:51:23.536
that they're going crazy?

477
00:51:23.579 --> 00:51:25.451
I don't know.

478
00:51:25.494 --> 00:51:26.974
I think there's far more people

479
00:51:27.018 --> 00:51:31.239
who think they know when
someone else is goin' crazy.


